// Regression: libFuzzer, 2026-04-17. Float literals exceeding float range
// (e.g. `1e99999`) threw std::out_of_range from std::stof, which was
// unhandled and aborted the process. Same bug class as the earlier stoi /
// stoul families — fixed with SafeParseFloat (bwsl_parser_soa.cpp).
pipeline P {
    const float X = 1e99999;
}
